> 
> BIC:
> Cliffjumper noticed how much Torca sounded like Prime, when he 
mentioned
> that famous line. How, interesting. He kept on roaring, moving 
slowly
> enough for the Beast to keep up.

::REDHOT::

    Redhot stirred a bit upon Torca's words. He attempted to sit up 
but the condition of his wings (never mind his wings THEMSELVES) kept 
him on his back. He grumbled loudly then sighed. 
    "That line of Torca's..." he said loud enough for Firedrill to 
hear. "Roll... out"... I beleive he said. I can't... put... a 
finger... on it". He caughed again. "Where does it come from?"
